c: 2
v: 258
t: "E a yi'aali on wennju…óo Ibraahiima e fii Jey…óo mo On, fii Alla no Ye…ói mo laamu, nde Ibraahiima maakunoo: \"Jey…óo lam on, ko On Wuurnata Wara\". [Wennju…óo on] wi'i: \"Min kadi mi…óo wuurna wara\". Ibraahiima maaki: \"Pellet Alla no Addira naange ngen fu…ónaange, addir nge hiirnaange\".Yeddu…óo on mugaa. Alla fewnataa yim…ìe too√±oo…ìe …ìen"